                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur">Mazmura Dāwit ‘Psalms of David’</title>
                     <note>Short prayer to Christ inserted into Ps. 118 after Gimel, <locus target="#109v"/>.
                        <q xml:lang="gez">ስብሐት፡ ለከ፡ ኦእግዚእየ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡</q>
                     The refrain of Ps. 135 (<locus target="#1"/>, <locus from="23r" to="123v"/>) has been added by a later hand.
                     Ps. 115 is numbered 116, Ps. 148 is numbered 147.
                     Ps. 130 is not numbered.</note>

                  </msItem>
