                        <seg type="rubrication">Divine names in <ref target="#ms_i1.4"/> and <ref target="#ms_i1.5"/> (<foreign xml:lang="gez">Māryām, tābot ba-warq</foreign>); 
                           numbers and titles of the Psalms, Canticles and Song of Songs; 
                           title of <ref target="#ms_i1.2"/> and <ref target="#ms_i1.3"/>; titles and refrains of <ref target="#ms_i1.4"/> and <ref target="#ms_i1.5"/>or their abbreviations; 
                           name, number and traditional explanation of the Hebrew letters in <ref target="#ms_i1.1">Ps. 118</ref>; 
                           elements of the punctuation signs and text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
